      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<span style=\"font-size: small\">A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad,f rom Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Abu Nasr, from Abdullah Bin Muhammad Al Shamy, from Al Husayn Bin Hanzala,</span> from one of the two (5th or 6th Imam<sup>asws</sup>) having said: ‘The gourd increases the mind’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn abu Nasr from ‘Abd Allah ibn Muhammad al-Shamiy from al-Husayn ibn Hanzalah who has said the following: “One of the two Imam, (abu Ja‘far or abu ‘Abd Allah), ‘Alayhim al-Salam, has said, ‘Gourd, squash increases al-Damagh (abilities of the brain).”’ "
        ]
      }
